<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span>重要股东大举甩卖洋河</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span>洋河股份</span>11 <span>月</span>23 <span>日晚间公告，江苏蓝色同盟股份有限公司于</span>2020 <span>年</span>11 <span>月</span>18 <span>日至</span>11 <span>月</span>20 <span>日通过大宗交易方式减持洋河股份股票</span>2262.67 <span>万股，占洋河股份总股本的</span>1.50% <span>。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201123/cc4c0a7723074b30b644211345df4d1f.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
